{{also|Yep|YEP}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Representing {{m|en|yeah}} pronounced with the {{l|en|[[mouth]] [[snapped]] [[closed]]}} at the end. Compare {{m|en|yup}}, {{m|en|nope}}, {{m|en|welp}}, and {{m|en|ope}}.
